Title: Bosch 1600A0015Z GDE 16 PLUS Professional Dust Extraction BSH600A0015Z
Description:
Bosch GDE 16 PLUS Professional Dust Extraction for virtually dust-free drilling with SDS-plus. Easy handling: connection to SDS-plus hammer and dust extractor with only one click. Works with all 2kg and 3kg Bosch SDS-plus hammers with a 50mm collar.

Max. Drilling Depth: 120mm.
Diameter of Bolt Circle: Max. 16mm; with core drilling Max. 82mm.
